COM.sootNsmoke.instructions
Class Instructions

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--COM.sootNsmoke.instructions.Instructions
Direct Known Subclasses:
SchemeCompiler
public class Instructions
extends java.lang.Object

A collection of static methods which are really just interfaces to the constructors for the classes in this package. If you make this class a superclass of yours, then you can write: aload(1) instead of new Aload(1) Most instructions have names like the standard mnemonics. For those which are also keywords (goto, new) an underscore is appended (goto_, new_).
